to federal court.

Mr. Angelos, owner of the Baltimore Orioles, has won major cases against th=
e=20
asbestos industry and represented Maryland in litigation against the tobacc=
o=20
industry.  John A. Pica, a lawyer in Mr. Angelos=0F' Baltimore firm, has be=
en=20
quoted saying Mr. Angelos plans to file 10 lawsuits this year against the=
