the proposed forfeiture should be eliminated or reduced.

FCC Gets =0F`Ahead of the Curve=0F' With Inquiry on Interactive TV

Although the market for high-speed interactive TV (ITV) services is in the=
=20
early stages of development, the FCC hopes to get =0F"ahead of the curve=0F=
" by=20
collecting information on the status of the ITV market and whether it shoul=
d=20
regulate it.

The FCC issued the notice of inquiry in Cable Services docket 01-7 because=
