have the incentive and ability to discriminate against unaffiliated ITV=20
service providers.=0F"

Commissioner Gloria Tristani supported the inquiry but =0F"regretted=0F" th=
at the=20
FCC issued an inquiry rather than a notice of proposed rulemaking.  =0F"Thi=
s=20
Commission must move promptly to ascertain the public interest in nascent=
