service, they predict.

=0F"We are deeply concerned about the incumbent long distance companies,=0F=
" said=20
Daniel P. Reingold, managing director-equity research for Credit Suisse Fir=
st=20
Boston Corp.  New entrants will be able to offer cut-rate service because=
