The Broadband Wireless Internet Forum has released two technical papers tha=
t=20
provide background and explanation of the technology advocated by the group=
. =20
The forum supports fixed broadband systems based on vector orthogonal=20
frequency division multiplexing (VOFDM).  The papers can be found at=20
http://www.bwif.org.

