information for consumers.=0F"

Under the biennial review process, =0F"ILEC service- quality requirements m=
ust=20
be based only upon a predicate of finding federal regulatory necessity in=
=20
light of meaningful competition and the public interest,=0F" Qwest Corp. sa=
id.  =0F"
This would exclude reporting elements claimed to  be =0F`useful=0F' or =0F`=
helpful.=0F'=0F" =20
The FCC should determine what the federal interest in service-quality=20
