 this=20
standard, Qwest said.

Service-quality reporting requirements are =0F"a perfect example of the typ=
e of=20
obsolete regulation that Congress had in mind when it enacted=0F" the bienn=
ial=20
review provisions of the Act, Verizon Communications Corp. said. =0F"Elimin=
