TR:  What about the expected turnover at the FCC?  How do you see that=20
affecting the Com-mission=0F's consideration of the MAG plan?

Brunner:  It could go a bunch of different ways.  You could get someone=20
coming in who says, =0F"A lot of real smart people spent a lot of time on t=
his,=20
and rather than reinvent the wheel, I=0F'm more inclined to support it.=0F"

Or you could get someone else who says, =0F"I don=0F't understand all this,=
